<plot>Documentary filmmaker, Stephen Larnell, travels to Dillan, Nebraska to investigate the spreading phenomenon of night school ninja classes. Stephen documents the experiences of Mark Rotane, a native Dillanite who is about to enroll in a 6 week ninja course at the local Ninco dojo. Beneath the Mask: Portrait of an American Ninja tells Mark's story, and explores the passions, dreams and struggles we all encounter in modern society.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?065208</url></doc>
